org.linqs.psl.model.rule.arithmetic

Class AbstractArithmeticRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.linqs.psl.model.rule.AbstractRule
      • org.linqs.psl.model.rule.arithmetic.AbstractArithmeticRule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Rule
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    UnweightedArithmeticRule, WeightedArithmeticRule

    public abstract class AbstractArithmeticRule
extends AbstractRule
    Base class for all (first order, i.e., not ground) arithmetic rules. Full equality checks (when two rules are the equal, but not the same reference) are expensive.
    Author:
    Stephen Bach
